  </developer>

  <description>
    <p>
      Manage your local Docker instance using a web UI.
    </p>
    <p>
      Before running the app make sure your user can access Docker CLI without root access.
    </p>
    <p>
      Features: 
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Start/Stop containers</li>
      <li>View container logs</li>
      <li>Volume management</li>
      <li>Resource allocation management</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
